revision.text: Possibly: The history of the growth and decay of the Othman empire. Part 1, Containing the Growth of the Othman Empire, from the reign of Othman the Founder, to the reign of Mahomet IV. That is, from the year 1300, to the Siege of Vienna, in 1683. Translated into English, from the author's own manuscript by N. Tindal.
